{"tid":801057,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"LINE下月推虛擬貨幣「LINK」　不涉ICO","createTime":"2018-08-31T10:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T06:23:29.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1a252399d1a26d18c04a4ed1295223f67f425a34","tid":801057,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535710608_b753.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535710608_b753.jpg&h=212a1072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n虛擬貨幣成行成市，除了耳熟能詳的比特幣之外，就連即時通訊軟件LINE都計劃推虛擬貨幣「LINK」。不過，LINK不會有首次代幣發行（ICO），而是邀請用戶透過使用LINE生態圈內的一系列指定服務而獲取LINK作為獎賞，並可以用作支付LINE生態圈內的各類服務，如內容、商貿、社交（Social）、遊戲、交易等。<br />\nLINK總發行額為10億個，當中的8億將作用戶獎賞之用，其餘的2億則會由LINK的發行者LINE Tech Plus管理並作儲備之用，9月將於虛擬貨幣交易平台BITBOX上市。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180831/58630089\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58630089&d=ZLoo38Xlgln5pGjbkuEY%2BIS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=6601106d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58630089&h=c62bfa73\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180831/58630089</a>"},{"pid":"6ae0b407e116fc0f4303e6bcd7856bf1e4df916b","tid":801057,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:01:12.000Z","msg":"睇錯<br />\n<br />\n以為LIHK長毛賊出虛擬貨幣"},{"pid":"e048e8e01247d2514b34be9c8606e882ba7c2bb4","tid":801057,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ae0b407e116fc0f4303e6bcd7856bf1e4df916b","tid":801057,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T11:01:12.000Z","msg":"睇錯<br />\n<br />\n以為LIHK長毛賊出虛擬貨幣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31